SolenopsisCampo Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you play "Tank Defender 2D"  or "Jumpy Tank"



PERSONAL INFORMATION WE COLLECT



When you play our game "Tank Defender 2D" or "Jumpy Tank", we (SolenopsisCampo Games) do not collect or use any of your personal information. 

However, Unity (our ad supplier) collects some information within the required data types to run their ads, to see what they collect please vists the following link: https://docs.unity.com/ads/GoogleDataSafety.html

Personalized ads are are available to opt-in but are turned off by default to comply with the GDPR and other policies.


MINORS

The games "Tank Defender 2D" and "JumpyTank" are suitable for all ages unless personalized ads have been turned on.



CHANGES

We may update this privacy policy from time to time in order to reflect, for example, changes to our practices or for other operational, legal or regulatory reasons.



CONTACT US

For more information about our privacy practices, if you have questions, or if you would like to make a complaint, please contact us by e-mail at yahammad.is.the.smartest@gmail.com or by mail using the details provided below:



